name: Stonks on ETH
description: Stonks is a memecoin inspired by the iconic Stonks meme. Stonks is more than just a token though; it's a community owned and community-driven project where you can thrive being part of a likeminded community. Our token is designed to bring the spirit of the Stonks meme to the cryptocurrency world, creating opportunities for everyone to be part of the next big meme revolution.
